    dc:description "FIGURES 13a–h. Tephritis formosa: a—habitus (lectotype) ♀; b—wing; c—tip of aculeus, ventral view; d—aculeus, ventral view; e—eversible membrane, ventral view; f—spermathecae; g—glans of phallus, lateral; h—epandrium, posterior view. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
